headline.print_headline: Daimler CEO Says Renschler Cannot Join Competitor Soon
headline.main: Daimler CEO Says Renschler Cannot Join Competitor Soon

lead_paragraph: Andreas Renschler, the former Daimler executive who resigned unexpectedly earlier this week, will not be able to join a competitor soon, Daimler Chief Executive Dieter Zetsche said on Thursday.
